org.palladiosimulator.experimentautomation.experiments

Interface InitialModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, EObject, Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InitialModelImpl

    public interface InitialModel
extends org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject
    A representation of the model object 'Initial Model'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Usage Model
    • Allocation
    • Middleware Repository
    • Event Middle Ware Repository
    • Reconfiguration Rules
    • Monitor Repository
    • Service Level Objectives
    • Repository
    • System
    • Resource Environment
    • Usage Evolution
    See Also:
    ExperimentsPackage.getInitialModel()
